Package: nat
Version: @VERSION@
Section: science
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-numpy, python3-pandas, python3-pyarrow, python3-matplotlib
Recommends: tmux, xdg-utils
Maintainer: NAT Team <nat@diamondapps.ch>
Description: NAT quantitative research terminal
 NAT is a quantitative research platform for extracting alpha signals from
 Hyperliquid perpetual futures. This package ships the `nat` CLI, the Python
 analysis stack, the release Rust binaries (ingestor, API, natviz3d), and the
 default configuration under /etc/nat.
